        "Text": {
          "type": "cexolocstring",
          "value": {
            "0": "Equipment with bonuses to magic skills like Evocation and Alteration improves the effectivenss of those classes of spells. Every spell utilizes these stats differently but you can expect to see improved damage, better healing, and generally better results the higher your equipment bonus."
          }
        }
