        "Text": {
          "type": "cexolocstring",
          "value": {
            "0": "Mana is a representation of your inner ability to cast magical spells. This is a limited resource which recharges naturally over time. Every time you cast a spell, a small portion of your mana is consumed.\n\nYou can increase your mana by purchasing perks and raising your Intelligence, Wisdom, and Charisma attributes. It can also be increased with equipment."
